        {
            "title": "歐股個別發展   英股六連升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">歐洲主要股市收市個別發展。歐洲央行議息後維持利率不變，符合市場預期，消息公布後，歐股升幅縮窄。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：德國證交所官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250306_FI_source-web_eu-stock-4.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：德國證交所官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250306_FI_source-web_eu-stock-4.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：德國證交所官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">泛歐指數Stoxx 600收市反彈0.24%，報551點，盤中最多曾漲0.69%，為連升兩日。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">德國DAX指數報24295點，升55點，升幅0.2%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">法國CAC指數報7818點，跌32點，跌幅0.4%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英國富時100指數報9138點，升76點，升幅0.85%，連升6個交易日。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">意大利富時MIB指數收報40599點，滑落0.24%或97點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">西班牙IBEX 35指數收報14256點，進賬1.34%或188點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15120127-%e6%ad%90%e8%82%a1%e5%80%8b%e5%88%a5%e7%99%bc%e5%b1%95-%e8%8b%b1%e8%82%a1%e5%85%ad%e9%80%a3%e5%8d%87",
